Cyberpunk style: A vast digital archive visualization in a neon-lit void, showing thousands of glowing data cubes arranged in a towering grid formation. Most cubes pulse with dim red light indicating restricted access, while exactly 77 cubes scattered throughout blaze with brilliant cyan, representing accessible documents. A lone figure in a sleek visor stands at the base, their reflection casting on a dark glossy floor. Holographic category filters materialize as floating geometric rings that reorganize the cubes—the cyan ones smoothly clustering together into an efficient vertical column while the red ones fade into the background haze. Digital particle streams connect the accessible cubes like synaptic pathways. The atmosphere is dense with floating code fragments and permission matrices rendered as intricate circuit patterns. Deep purple and electric blue gradients dominate the background, with sharp neon accents highlighting the dramatic reorganization of data from chaos to order.
